      readMore: "Preview tomorrow's Harvey biography (7.9) by asking what it would take to actually prove blood moves in a circle rather than just sitting still in the body.",
      connect: "Scripture again and again ties blood to life itself — the very fact this lesson has spent all morning exploring in cellular detail.",
